    <br>
    <p>The Liu laboratory engineers nano- and micro-materials to address current challenges in drug delivery and tissue engineering. We design novel self-assembly processes to synthesize nano- and microparticles with well-controlled features to target delivery and sustain release of the drug compunds and therapeutic cells to the disease sites.</p>
